title: Full HD 1080P 16MP Digital Video Camcorder Camera DV DVR 2.7” TFT LCD 16x ZOOM US plug
detail:
High Definition: COMS Sensor camera, max to 16.0 Mega pixels. LED fill light, white balance and light exposure settings to adjust the light of pictures and make sure you can record high quality clear pictures and videos.
External Memory With Card Slot: SD/HCSD card (32GB Max) available for connecting TVs(SD card is not included). 
Lightweight And Portable: Lightweight,small and exquisite camcorder(8.82oz/250g,4.53*1.89*1.97inches/115*48*50mm); Easy to carry and store, perfect to be a gift and record your special lovely moments.
2.7" TFT LCD Display: Bright and clearly visible, even outdoors in the sun. Built-in anti-shake technology helps you avoid getting a blurred picture or video.
Night Light And 16X Digital Zoom: Light up the scene during night time; capture image or video with details; ideal for formal ceremonies, sports outdoor games and wild life.

title: Cherry Mobile Flare S7 Plus
detail: The Cherry Mobile Flare S7 Plus packs a 16MP + 5MP main camera and a 16MP front-facing camera for selfies. This device is powered by a MediaTek Helio P60 SoC accompanied by a 3050mAh battery.

title: Samsung Galaxy S10+
detail: The Samsung Galaxy S10+ is packed with a 6.4" Quad HD+ Dynamic AMOLED Infinity-O Display, SD855/Exynos 9820 SoC, 8/12GB RAM, an on-screen fingerprint sensor, reverse-wireless charging, and a 4,100mAh battery.
